<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">

        <style>
            body{
                padding: 0;
                margin: 0;
                background-color: floralwhite ;
            }
            h1{
                margin-top:50px;
                margin-left: 510px;
                font-size: 60px;
                font-family: 'Karla',sans-serif;
                font-weight: lighter;
            }
            .slider-frame{
                overflow:hidden;
                height: 800px;
                width: 800px;
                margin-left: 360px;
                margin-top:20px;
            }
            @-webkit-keyframes slide_animation{
                0%{left:0px;}
                10%{left:0px;}
                20%{left:1200px;}
                30%{left:1200px;}
                40%{left:2400px;}
                50%{left:2400px;}
                60%{left:1200px;}
                70%{left:1200px;}
                80%{left:0px;}
                90%{left:0px;}
                100%{left:0px;}
            }
            .slide-images{
                width: 3600px;
                height: 800px;
                margin: 0 0 0 -2400px;
                position: relative;
                -webkit-animation-name: slide_animation;
                -webkit-animation-duration:33s ;
                -webkit-animation-iteration-count: infinite;
                -webkit-animation-direction: alternate ;
                -webkit-animation-play-state: running ;
            }
            .img-container{
                height: 800px;
                width: 1200px;
                position: relative;
                float: left;
            }
            img{
                height: 800px;
                width: 800px;
            }
        </style>

    </head>
<body>
    <h1>Sliding images</h1>
    <div class="slider-frame">
        <div class="slide-images">
            <div class="img-container">
                <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
            </div>
            <div class="img-container">
                <img src="https://www.ricksdailytips.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/ibuypower-desktop-gaming-pc.jpg">  </div>
            <div class="img-container">
                <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>



</body>

</html>
